Docs.summary: Listener for events relating to a SIP call, such as when a call is being received ("on ringing") or a call is outgoing ("on calling").

remarks.para: Listener for events relating to a SIP call, such as when a call is being received ("on ringing") or a call is outgoing ("on calling").
Many of these events are also received by SipSession.Listener.
